    "serotonin_payoff_number": 83957,
    "phase_1": "Aapka poora din barbaad ho jaata hai, bas ek galati ki wajah se!",
    "phase_2": "Aur aapko pata bhi nahi chalta woh kya hai?",
    "phase_3": "Mujhe bhi lagta tha meri productivity kam hai, ya main lazy hoon. Subah uthta tha, mobile check kiya, email, social media... aur phir poore din stress. Main aap jaisa hi tha, hamesha short-term hacks dhundhta rehta tha. Sochta tha koi special coffee, ya naya app meri life badal dega. Par asli problem kahin aur thi, jo hum sab nazarandaaz kar dete hain.",
    "phase_4": "Yeh ek galati hai dopamine hijack. Subah uthte hi phone ya stimulants se jo ekdam se dopamine boost milta hai, woh aapke din bhar ki motivation ko khatam kar deta hai. Brain overstimulated ho jaata hai!",
    "phase_5": "Toh agle 83957 dino tak subah uthte hi pehle ek ghante tak screen se door raho. Kyunki aapka poora din barbaad ho jaata hai, bas ek galati ki wajah se \u2014 aur woh hai subah ka yeh galat shuruaat."
